column5: I'm heading to the Bay early February with Sherriff and some other hooligans. I was wondering if anyone up that way could let me know how the thickness/depth is coming along. We're going to Hyatt's so if anyone knows if he's got huts out now...... Thanks  Corn Nug
Relax Andy, I talked to Rob, he told me to tell you to RELAX!!!  There will be lots...  Sherriff
Hahahaha..... Thanks Jeff. I'm just getting excited about the trip, the date's closing in. Tell Rob I want the hut that's been placed above the pickerel hang out.  Corn Nug
Yes his huts are on the way out, we're going up Friday at lunch, he says he will be ready.
Good luck and look forward to your report.  Andy, it'll be a good trip.  Sherriff
